HEADWORD: Tenantry
<hw>Ten"ant*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
body of tenants; <as>as, the <ex>tenantry</ex> of a manor or a
kingdom</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Tenancy.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
